title: The Last Show of 2020!
description: We test Dave's wife Susan to see if she can guess the word of bleeped out Christmas songs, a Group Therapy with a girl who got her co-worker/crush a present and now doesn't know what to think, she check in with the girls we've been talking to weekly to see if they are engaged yet, reacting to bad presents, and more!
